column6: (Two SampleID can have same SubjectID, eg. Oral wash and matched BAL. For rest the field is NA)
column7: (Positive control like spiked phage or negative control status like water etc.)
column8: (Extra comments for sample, eg. Longitudnal sample)
column16: (Y for disease, N for no disease, NA for controls )
